    <main>
        <h2 class="section-title">Tech Stack & Skills</h2>
        <p><strong>Languages & Tools:</strong> Java, Kotlin, Python, SAP ABAP, SQL, Git & GitHub</p>
        <p><strong>Areas:</strong> Mobile Programming (Android), Machine Learning (ANN, LSTM), Database Management, Object-Oriented Programming</p>

        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top: 50px;">Featured Projects</h2>
        
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-tag">Python & Deep Learning</span>
                <h3>Stock Market Optimization (Deep Learning)</h3>
                <p>I developed hybrid artificial neural network models to increase and optimize stock market price prediction accuracy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-tag">Kotlin & Android</span>
                <h3>UniApp</h3>
                <p>A centralized mobile application project developed collaboratively with my teammates to track and manage intra-university events simultaneously. It includes Room DB integration.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-tag">SAP ABAP</span>
                <h3>Innovation Idea Management System</h3>
                <p>A corporate system infrastructure designed to track and evaluate ideas presented by employees for continuous improvement.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <span class="card-tag">IoT Device</span>
                <h3>Wi-Fi Controlled Air Quality Monitor</h3>
                <p>A device that measures air quality based on the data received from its sensor according to the alcohol density in the air.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

